Description: Name of tennis tournament in which match occurred.

Round of named tournament in which match occurred.
F = Finals
SF = Semifinals
QF = Quarterfinals
R16 = Round of 16
R32 = Round of 32
R64 = Round of 64
R128 = Round of 128
Surface the match was played on. Either Hard, Clay, or Grass.
Number of service games (i.e. games) in the match.
Number of aces in the match.
